data.description: Unlock the door to this remarkable home in coveted Madison Cove!  All of the upgrades you could ask for including a hidden walk-in pantry and extra large covered back patio! Trendy open concept with huge island, granite, crown molding, stainless appliances, and more will make your new home the talk of the town! Primary and guest suites on main with a massive laundry room.  Primary bedroom includes a door to the back patio and bath has the proper water closet everyone wants! Walk in attic and pull down storage too! Oversized bonus room includes a gorgeous wet bar. Fully fenced back yard. Seller is offering 1% toward buyer's points with acceptable offer. Second upstairs primary suite has two closets! All closets have built ins.  All baths/showers have glass doors so no shower curtains are needed. All bedrooms have their own bath! All sides brick! This one is missing nothing!
